title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2011 Mar 15 TU [sebaygo1]

The Peter Schiff Show
Tuesday, 15 March 2011


[sebaygo1]


Tuesday's guest is Wayne Root, 2008 Libertarian vice presidential nominee & host of "The Wayne Allyn Root Show," on March Madness (Wayne's also a professional sports handicapper), why tsunamis aren't stimulus projects, and how President Obama could be expected to resolve the NFL lockout.
